name: Quatern AI
description:
The mission of Quatern.ai is to democratize the field of artificial intelligence through the power of collective effort and blockchain technology. By facilitating a platform where AI models can be combined to enhance their predictive capabilities, Quatern.ai aims to break down the barriers of AI development and create a more inclusive and powerful ecosystem. This mission is rooted in the belief that the best AI solutions arise not from isolated models but from the collaborative fusion of diverse AI intelligences.

Our vision for Quatern.ai is to be at the forefront of an AI revolution that is participative, transparent, and rewards each contributor fairly. We envision a future where Quatern.ai empowers individuals and organizations around the globe to solve some of the most pressing data science challenges, from improving healthcare diagnostics to refining environmental models and optimizing financial systems.

The goals of Quatern.ai are clear: to establish a decentralized platform that encourages and facilitates the contribution of AI models, to implement a fair and transparent token-based reward system, and to ensure that every participant, regardless of their background, has a voice in the platform's governance.

The benefits of joining the Quatern.ai project are manifold. Contributors can monetize their AI models while retaining ownership, thanks to native token rewards. Users benefit from enhanced AI predictions through the collective intelligence of multiple models. Developers are provided with a transparent, secure, and efficient system for deploying their AI solutions. And all participants become part of a pioneering community at the intersection of AI and blockchain, shaping the future of technology with every contribution and decision.

Together, let us unleash the power of collective artificial intelligence on Cardano!

name: Linkage Finance
description:
Cardano’s growing ecosystem becomes home to more and more projects and business ideas. While the enormous number of projects creates a flourishing ecosystem, it challenges investors. It gets increasingly difficult to invest in projects if the number is constantly rising.

The time needed to do diligent research is increasing and buying and selling tokens takes more time. As well, fees can drive costs up as Decentralized Exchanges demand fees in addition to Cardano network fees. A Decentralized Fund approach can avoid the problems mentioned above, by simplifying the process of investing in the broad market. By leveraging smart contracts, the community can create a non-custodial, transparent fund that guarantees a one-to-one backing with its real value and the option to withdraw the underlying assets at any point.

It’s time to bring easy and hurdle-free ways of investing to the blockchain world and work with the community towards an easily accessible ecosystem.
